{% comment %}
Routing Playground — app-wide base view. Every room extends this and
overrides only the blocks it needs.

Block contract:
  status   — a permanent reminder of the four tiers + a little world readout.
  heading  — room title; default = state.description.
  body     — the lesson content.
  choices  — the action menu (always visible).
  footer   — optional bottom line.
{% endcomment %}
{% block status %}tiers: synonym › template › semantic › local-LLM › main-LLM   |   lamp: {% if world.lamp %}on{% else %}off{% endif %}   |   budget: {{ world.budget }}{% endblock %}

{% block heading %}{{ state.description }}{% endblock %}

{% block body %}{% endblock %}

{% block choices %}{% endblock %}
{% block footer %}{% endblock %}
